Package norswap.violin

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Copyable
    An interface analogous to the Kotlin version of Cloneable, except that Copyable.copy is public and that Copyable.copycast is available for effortless casting.
    Stack<T>
    A fairly classical stack interface, conspicuously missing from both Java and Kotlin stdlibs.
